question: Please provide me the number of medications covered by the payer with the ID 8fa6c185-e44e-3e34-8bd8-39be8694f4ce.
What is the SNOMED code of the encounter df1757dd-8021-2c04-c82c-ed437cd7f155?
answers:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> 
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> 
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> 
PREFIX uuid: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#urn:uuid> 
PREFIX snomed: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#snomed:SNOMED-CT>
SELECT ?snomed 
WHERE 
{ 
   ?encounter a syn:Encounter ; 
              syn:id 'df1757dd-8021-2c04-c82c-ed437cd7f155'^^uuid: ; 
              syn:code ?snomed . 
   FILTER (isliteral(?snomed)) 
   FILTER (regex(str(?snomed), "^urn:uuid"))
}

question: Please provide me the patients who have received the immunization with code 140.

question: Who is the patient associated with the claim cca769d0-09e0-72f9-23aa-e6ddb2200792?
Please provide me the number of immunizations uncovered by the payer Cigna Health.
answers:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX pl: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral> 
SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?immunization) AS ?uncovered_immunizations) WHERE { 
  ?immunization a syn:Immunization.
  ?immunization syn:patientId ?patient. 
  ?patient syn:payer ?payer. 
  ?payer syn:name 'Cigna Health'^^pl.
  FILTER NOT EXISTS {?payer syn:covered_immunizations ?immunization}.
}
